OL,6,FA new framework to prevent and respond
OL,7,Fto gender-based violence (GBV) in
OL,8,Fschools has been launched.
OL,10,FThe framework, developed by the
OL,11,FScottish Government, Rape Crisis
OL,12,FScotland and Zero Tolerance, sets out
OL,13,Fhow schools can use education to
OL,14,Ftackle GBV.
