OL,3,CFramework to help schools tackle
OL,4,Cgender-based violence launched
OL,6,FGBV refers to behaviours ranging from
OL,7,Fname calling, intimidation and
OL,8,Fphysical violence to sexual harassment
OL,9,Fand emotional abuse which can affect
OL,10,Fanyone but is more commonly
OL,11,Fexperienced by women and girls.
OL,13,FFirst Minister of Scotland Humza
OL,14,FYousaf and Scottish Education
OL,15,FSecretary Jenny Gilruth unveiled the
OL,16,Fframework during a visit to Moffat
OL,17,FAcademy in Dumfries and Galloway on
OL,18,FMonday 4 March.
