OL,3,CFramework to help schools tackle
OL,4,Cgender-based violence launched
OL,6,FIt aims to demonstrate the ways GBV
OL,7,Fcan affect young people, provide
OL,8,Fguidance to support schools' responses
OL,9,Fto GBV, and signpost to further
OL,10,Fsupport and learning.
OL,12,FIt follows the publication of the
OL,13,FBehaviour in Scottish Schools Research
OL,14,Freport last year which highlighted an
OL,15,Fincrease in misogynistic views and
OL,16,Flanguage as an emerging concern in
OL,17,Fschools.
