OL,3,CFramework to help schools tackle
OL,4,Cgender-based violence launched
OL,6,FThe First Minister said: "We want
OL,7,Fschools to create cultures in which
OL,8,Fall members of the school community
OL,9,Fknow that gender-based violence is
OL,10,Funacceptable and will not be
OL,11,Ftolerated. Prevention and early
OL,12,Fintervention are key to the approach
OL,13,Fto address the underlying causes of
OL,14,Fgender-based violence, particularly
OL,15,Fgender inequality.
OL,17,F"All children and young people have a
OL,18,Fright to a learning environment where
OL,19,Fthey are protected, cared for and in
OL,20,Fwhich their rights and needs are
OL,21,Frespected."
