OL,3,CFramework to help schools tackle
OL,4,Cgender-based violence launched
OL,6,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,7,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,8,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,9,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,11,FEducation Secretary Jenny Gilruth
OL,12,Fsaid: "There is no place for
OL,13,Fharassment or abuse in any form in our
OL,14,Fschools and this framework aims to
OL,15,Fprovide support for everyone in a
OL,16,Fschool community to recognise it as it
OL,17,Foccurs and be equipped to respond
OL,18,Fappropriately. "
OL,20,FThe ministers met staff and students
OL,21,Fas part of their visit.
