OL,3,CFramework to help schools tackle
OL,4,Cgender-based violence launched
OL,6,FPupil Morgan Todd said: "As a young
OL,7,Fwoman, I would hate to feel there were
OL,8,Fany limits placed on my aspirations or
OL,9,Fon those of any girl at Moffat Academy.
OL,11,F"Gender equality is about living in a
OL,12,Ffair society where everyone is valued
OL,13,Ffor their talents rather than judged
OL,14,Fby their gender. At Moffat Academy, I
OL,15,Ffeel everyone gets the chance to write
OL,16,Ftheir own story- no matter their
OL,17,Fbackground or gender- helping to
OL,18,Fprepare us for life after school in
OL,19,Fmodern Scotland."
